        <num>CC 2610</num>
        <heading>2610.  Cure of nonconformity</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2610.  Cure of nonconformity
Upon rejection of nonconforming things by the buyer, the seller may cure the nonconformity when the time for performance has not yet expired or when the seller had a reasonable belief that the nonconforming things would be acceptable to the buyer.  In such a case the seller must give reasonable notice of his intention to cure to the buyer.</p>
        </content>
